Title: Spontaneous N=2 --> N=1 local supersymmetry breaking with surviving

local gauge groupAuthors: P. Fre', L. Girardello, I. Pesando, M. Trigiante

Comments: 17 pages, 1 Textype, 2 Postscript figures

Journal-ref: Nucl.Phys. B493 (1997) 231-248

Generic partial supersymmetry breaking of $N=2$ supergravity with zero vacuumenergy and with surviving unbroken arbitrary gauge groups is exhibited.Specific examples are given.